Package: bakerrr
Title: Background-parallel jobs in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Anirban", "Shaw", , "anirbanshaw24@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4021-513X"))
Description: Run background-parallel jobs in R using.  Provides flexible
    utilities to launch, track, and control any R function as a parallel
    background process, with robust status, error, and result monitoring.
